data: This project involves the development of 2.08 hectares of development land at Kingmoor Park, Carlisle to provide 5,058 m² (54,444 ft²) of speculative business workspace. The proposal is to provide nineteen individual business units of varying sizes (144 m² - 421 m²) designed to offer high quality modern business space providing ideal grow on space for high growth SME’s in the Cumbria LEP area.
